hort form <i>Bob</i> is very common, but <i>Hob</i> and <i>Dob</i>, which were common in the Middle Ages and gave rise to surnames, are extinct.  See also  Rupert ."],"variants":[]}],"lifeSummary":"Robert Grantte was born in 1461, in Allington, Lincolnshire, England, United Kingdom. He married Isolel Ross in 1483, in Allington, Lincolnshire, England, United Kingdom. They were the parents of at least 1 son. He died in 1569, in his hometown, at the age of 108."},"et":{"1461–1569":"1461–1569","1463–1530":"1463–1530","1497–1569":"1497–1569","1569":"1569","ABT 1483":"1483","1497":"1497","1530":"1530","1463":"1463","1461":"1461","Quadring, Lincolnshire, England":"Quadring, Lincolnshire, England","Allington, Lincolnshire, England, United Kingdom":"Allington, Lincolnshire, Inglismaa, United Kingdom"},"fi":{"1461–1569":"1461–1569","1463–1530":"1463–1530","1497–1569":"1497–1569","1569":"1569","ABT 1483":"1483","1497":"1497","1530":"1530","1463":"1463","1461":"1461","Quadring, Lincolnshire, England":"Quadring, Lincolnshire, England","Allington, Lincolnshire, England, United Kingdom":"Allington, Lincolnshire, Englanti, Yhdistynyt kuningaskunta"},"fr":{"1461–1569":"1461–1569","1463–1530":"1463–1530","1497–1569":"1497–1569","1569":"1569","ABT 1483":"1483","1497":"1497","1530":"1530","1463":"1463","1461":"1461","Quadring, Lincolnshire, England":"Quadring, Lincolnshire, Angleterre","Allington, Lincolnshire, England, United Kingdom":"Allington, Lincolnshire, Angleterre, Royaume-Uni","lifeSummary":"Robert Grantte est né en 1461, à Allington, Lincolnshire, Angleterre, Royaume-Uni. Il a épousé Isolel Ross en 1483, à Allington, Lincolnshire, Angleterre, Royaume-Uni. Ils ont eu au moins 1 fils. Il est décédé en 1569, dans sa ville natale, à l’âge de 108 ans."},"de":{"1461–1569":"1461–1569","1463–1530":"1463–1530","1497–1569":"1497–1569","1569":"1569","ABT 1483":"1483","1497":"1497","1530":"1530","1463":"1463","1461":"1461","Quadring, Lincolnshire, England":"Quadring, Lincolnshire, Englan